window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Lorenzo Damiani. Tall. Dark. Handsome. Seductive. Enigmatic. Dominant. He was my knight in shining armor that fateful morning in Naples.</p> <p>When he invited me to his tiny Italian island paradise, I was too far under his spell to say no. For one full week, I was uninhibitedly his. No ties. No pressure. The best-laid plans...</p> <p>Now, I'm back home in Seattle. I'm definitely tied...and the pressure is on. I have a tiny surprise that will last forever.</p> <p>But Lorenzo is the heir to a dark legacy he wants no part of. What will he do when he finds out he has an heir of his own?</p> <p><b>Contains mature themes.</b></p>"; 
